  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nWhen Status installed from a 'public chat registration' referral link - we show 'Accept and Join' view which. When tap on Accept button - user is redirected to public chat. However, there is no top bar neither bottom tabs bar. To navigate back possible only via hardware Back button though. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nTop chat bar with 'Back' button and bottom tab bar are present after joining to referral public chat\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nNo top chat bar with 'Back' button and bottom tab bar  after joining to referral public chat\r\n![Image from iOS (36)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/125300370-a02b6300-e332-11eb-9ec2-7bb6dac82e1d.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Install Status\r\n- Open Status from the 'public chat registration' referral link\r\n- Create new account till the 'Accept and join' view is opened\r\n- Tap 'Accept and Join' button\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n- Status version: release 1.15 \r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n",
