    "body": "This issue was due to the test referral link we use for testing. \r\nWhen release build installed from PlayStore which reached by referral link redirect, then `Accept and Join` view appears on Chats view where top bar and bottom tabs bar are present (not like here in the scenario when this view appears on the top on Notification Enable screen)\r\nAnd so in that case top|bottom bars will be present. \r\nClosing this issue because all is OK for those who install release from Play Store.",
